{"tid":1504152,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"荃葵青遊行 逃生路線 休息站 ！推定先","createTime":"2019-08-25T08:33:59.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-25T11:42:54.000Z","uid":222970,"like":80,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":115,"replies":[{"pid":"f8d8f8da8012e3df43ddb93d733e1c56aa09f674","tid":1504152,"uid":222970,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T08:33:59.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">萬一出左事 推呢個post上熱門<br />\n第一首要大家提供資料俾義士逃離戰區<br />\n</span></span><br />\n8.25即時【荃葵青區教會休息站】<br />\n<br />\n以下教會於今天（8月25日）開放予有需要人士，為大家提供休息、禱告、補給等身心靈支援。<br />\n<br />\n1. 基立浸信會<br />\n葵涌信芳街41號悦龍大廈二樓2B座<br />\n時間：1500 - 2200<br />\n電話：24258080 方牧師<br />\n<a href=\"https://goo.gl/maps/EuDCRaeFhFQKXzBcA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgoo.gl%2Fmaps%2FEuDCRaeFhFQKXzBcA&d=6v%2BmLhPCoO19KIzpXGl1Dv2x0mEA6i1FZlyL0j1bjmE%3D&h=a1326569\" target=\"_blank\">https://goo.gl/maps/EuDCRaeFhFQKXzBcA</a><br />\n-<br />\n2. 顯恩浸信會<br />\n荃灣大河道99號99廣場20樓<br />\n時間：1500 - 2000<br />\n電話：24028327<br />\n*由牧者主領祈禱會下午4:45-5:15<br />\n<a href=\"https://goo.gl/maps/RoxKFYqgnbcKm9xdA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgoo.gl%2Fmaps%2FRoxKFYqgnbcKm9xdA&d=6v%2BmLhPCoO19KIzpXGl1Dv2x0mEA6i1FZlyL0j1bjmE%3D&h=621ab2bd\" target=\"_blank\">https://goo.gl/maps/RoxKFYqgnbcKm9xdA</a><br />\n-<br />\n3. 基督教香港信義會天恩堂<br />\n葵涌葵盛圍364號<br />\n時間：1500 - 2000（按需要延長）<br />\n電話：24805833<br />\n*提供簡單護理<br />\n*每小時首15分鐘有祈禱聚會<br />\n<a href=\"https://goo.gl/maps/kzmMqCaqhDBxLj758\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgoo.gl%2Fmaps%2FkzmMqCaqhDBxLj758&d=6v%2BmLhPCoO19KIzpXGl1Dv2x0mEA6i1FZlyL0j1bjmE%3D&h=c4bf8508\" target=\"_blank\">https://goo.gl/maps/kzmMqCaqhDBxLj758</a><br />\n-<br />\n4. 聖公會荊冕堂<br />\n荃灣德士古道67號<br />\n時間：1600 開始<br />\n電話：26145321<br />\n*有醫療站及「馬拉松泰澤祈禱-身心靈休息站」<br />\n<a href=\"https://goo.gl/maps/oHtRFNt5K4g3NtfUA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgoo.gl%2Fmaps%2FoHtRFNt5K4g3NtfUA&d=6v%2BmLhPCoO19KIzpXGl1Dv2x0mEA6i1FZlyL0j1bjmE%3D&h=a1a23cc5\" target=\"_blank\">https://goo.gl/maps/oHtRFNt5K4g3NtfUA</a><br />\n-<br />\n5. 中華基督教會全完堂<br />\n荃灣大屋街2-4號（近荃新天地一期）<br />\n時間：1430 - 1800（按實際情況，請留意更新）<br />\n電話：24922866<br />\n1430起每小時有祈禱會<br />\n<a href=\"https://goo.gl/maps/EyhVrdXMAvYT4G9CA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgoo.gl%2Fmaps%2FEyhVrdXMAvYT4G9CA&d=6v%2BmLhPCoO19KIzpXGl1Dv2x0mEA6i1FZlyL0j1bjmE%3D&h=b884ffeb\" target=\"_blank\">https://goo.gl/maps/EyhVrdXMAvYT4G9CA</a><br />\n-<br />\n6. 荃灣浸信會 <br />\n荃灣青山道99-113號<br />\n時間：照常時間 收1730<br />\n電話：24980378<br />\n<a href=\"https://goo.gl/maps/RxgFaZc69jWgE5GQ9\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgoo.gl%2Fmaps%2FRxgFaZc69jWgE5GQ9&d=6v%2BmLhPCoO19KIzpXGl1Dv2x0mEA6i1FZlyL0j1bjmE%3D&h=02e98b07\" target=\"_blank\">https://goo.gl/maps/RxgFaZc69jWgE5GQ9</a><br />\n-<br />\n7. 基督教主恩會 <br />\n荃灣青山道455-457號華懋荃灣廣場四樓<br />\n時間：1500 - 1700 守望禱告<br />\n會按特定情況 延長開放時間<br />\n電話：24067793<br />\n<a href=\"https://goo.gl/maps/bBJhW8Hzrtg5ewsy5\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgoo.gl%2Fmaps%2FbBJhW8Hzrtg5ewsy5&d=6v%2BmLhPCoO19KIzpXGl1Dv2x0mEA6i1FZlyL0j1bjmE%3D&h=b4274434\" target=\"_blank\">https://goo.gl/maps/bBJhW8Hzrtg5ewsy5</a><br />\n-<br />\n8. 麗城浸信會 <br />\n荃灣麗城花園二期商場231室<br />\n時間：1630 - 1730有祈禱會<br />\n電話：24144848<br />\n<a href=\"https://goo.gl/maps/F3PYQN9uD5TczzG3A\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgoo.gl%2Fmaps%2FF3PYQN9uD5TczzG3A&d=6v%2BmLhPCoO19KIzpXGl1Dv2x0mEA6i1FZlyL0j1bjmE%3D&h=2956b830\" target=\"_blank\">https://goo.gl/maps/F3PYQN9uD5TczzG3A</a><br />\n-<br />\n9. 天主教聖多默宗徒堂<br />\n青衣青綠街5號<br />\n時間：1600 - 2000<br />\n電話：24322933<br />\n<a href=\"https://goo.gl/maps/Gf514zWuUVtMx1Uj6\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgoo.gl%2Fmaps%2FGf514zWuUVtMx1Uj6&d=6v%2BmLhPCoO19KIzpXGl1Dv2x0mEA6i1FZlyL0j1bjmE%3D&h=ff963c2d\" target=\"_blank\">https://goo.gl/maps/Gf514zWuUVtMx1Uj6</a><br />\n.<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n資料來源：香港基督教教牧聯署籌委會、8.25荃葵青大遊行頻道"},{"pid":"96f6d68fe3d85d0a0391d4a40c90a5ea962c570e","tid":1504152,"uid":222970,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T08:35:56.000Z","msg":"各位提供定資訊 盡量將有用資訊置頂<br />\n唔好推住先"},{"pid":"135b249f0f3c9530e903e5e5aa5583dc3019dafc","tid":1504152,"uid":241567,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T08:40:07.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"6331fafee7b1d76fad5398ab663c03de96abb90f","tid":1504152,"uid":273670,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T08:41:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3bc38b4b2869756d5c0fd9c088537575fd11da05","tid":1504152,"uid":122122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T08:41:35.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f4769393ef7981daac18b69750b97ec56bae84cd","tid":1504152,"uid":30115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T08:42:06.000Z","msg":"推呀"},{"pid":"251b3331cc6f9d7ed5cfd86db0aa2d692ecd04cc","tid":1504152,"uid":235535,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T08:42:30.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b197c216b368097c9b29ea9545fc248a8f9ac251","tid":1504152,"uid":29899,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T08:42:35.000Z","msg":"日期: 2019．9．1<br />\n時間: 13:00<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">#黑警還眼 #612 #721 #811 #823</span></strong></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/k7wVcXg.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fk7wVcXg.jpg&h=05fc61c8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YyFriWu.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYyFriWu.jpg&h=47e393ba&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n[9．1機場] 官逼民反，民不得不反<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/dJNfyS\" data-auto-link target