tps://goo.gl/maps/RoxKFYqgnbcKm9xdA</a><br />\n-<br />\n3. 基督教香港信義會天恩堂<br />\n葵涌葵盛圍364號<br />\n時間：1500 - 2000（按需要延長）<br />\n電話：24805833<br />\n*提供簡單護理<br />\n*每小時首15分鐘有祈禱聚會<br />\n<a href=\"https://goo.gl/maps/kzmMqCaqhDBxLj758\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgoo.gl%2Fmaps%2FkzmMqCaqhDBxLj758&d=6v%2BmLhPCoO19KIzpXGl1Dv2x0mEA6i1FZlyL0j1bjmE%3D&h=c4bf8508\" target=\"_blank\">https://goo.gl/maps/kzmMqCaqhDBxLj758</a><br />\n-<br />\n4. 聖公會荊冕堂<br />\n荃灣德士古道67號<br />\n時間：1600 開始<br />\n電話：26145321<br />\n*有醫療站及「馬拉松泰澤祈禱-身心靈休息站」<br />\n<a href=\"https://goo.gl/maps/oHtRFNt5K4g3NtfUA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgoo.gl%2Fmaps%2FoHtRFNt5K4g3NtfUA&d=6v%2BmLhPCoO19KIzpXGl1Dv2x0mEA6i1FZlyL0j1bjmE%3D&h=a1a23cc5\" target=\"_blank\">https://goo.gl/maps/oHtRFNt5K4g3NtfUA</a><br />\n-<br />\n5. 中華基督教會全完堂<br />\n荃灣大屋街2-4號（近荃新天地一期）<br />\n時間：1430 - 1800（按實際情況，請留意更新）<br />\n電話：24922866<br />\n1430起每小時有祈禱會<br />\n<a href=\"https://goo.gl/maps/EyhVrdXMAvYT4G9CA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgoo.gl%2Fmaps%2FEyhVrdXMAvYT4G9CA&d=6v%2BmLhPCoO19KIzpXGl1Dv2x0mEA6i1FZlyL0j1bjmE%3D&h=b884ffeb\" target=\"_blank\">https://goo.gl/maps/EyhVrdXMAvYT4G9CA</a><br />\n-<br />\n6. 荃灣浸信會 <br />\n荃灣青山道99-113號<br />\n時間：照常時間 收1730<br />\n電話：24980378<br />\n<a href=\"https://goo.gl/maps/RxgFaZc69jWgE5GQ9\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgoo.gl%2Fmaps%2FRxgFaZc69jWgE5GQ9&d=6v%2BmLhPCoO19KIzpXGl1Dv2x0mEA6i1FZlyL0j1bjmE%3D&h=02e98b07\" target=\"_blank\">https://goo.gl/maps/RxgFaZc69jWgE5GQ9</a><br />\n-<br />\n7. 基督教主恩會 <br />\n荃灣青山道455-457號華懋荃灣廣場四樓<br />\n時間：1500 - 1700 守望禱告<br />\n會按特定情況 延長開放時間<br />\n電話：24067793<br />\n<a href=\"https://goo.gl/maps/bBJhW8Hzrtg5ewsy5\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgoo.gl%2Fmaps%2FbBJhW8Hzrtg5ewsy5&d=6v%2BmLhPCoO19KIzpXGl1Dv2x0mEA6i1FZlyL0j1bjmE%3D&h=b4274434\" target=\"_blank\">https://goo.gl/maps/bBJhW8Hzrtg5ewsy5</a><br />\n-<br />\n8. 麗城浸信會 <br />\n荃灣麗城花園二期商場231室<br />\n時間：1630 - 1730有祈禱會<br />\n電話：24144848<br />\n<a href=\"https://goo.gl/maps/F3PYQN9uD5TczzG3A\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgoo.gl%2Fmaps%2FF3PYQN9uD5TczzG3A&d=6v%2BmLhPCoO19KIzpXGl1Dv2x0mEA6i1FZlyL0j1bjmE%3D&h=2956b830\" target=\"_blank\">https://goo.gl/maps/F3PYQN9uD5TczzG3A</a><br />\n-<br />\n9. 天主教聖多默宗徒堂<br />\n青衣青綠街5號<br />\n時間：1600 - 2000<br />\n電話：24322933<br />\n<a href=\"https://goo.gl/maps/Gf514zWuUVtMx1Uj6\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgoo.gl%2Fmaps%2FGf514zWuUVtMx1Uj6&d=6v%2BmLhPCoO19KIzpXGl1Dv2x0mEA6i1FZlyL0j1bjmE%3D&h=ff963c2d\" target=\"_blank\">https://goo.gl/maps/Gf514zWuUVtMx1Uj6</a><br />\n.<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n資料來源：香港基督教教牧聯署籌委會、8.25荃葵青大遊行頻道"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T10:49:48.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"4a3c4db8a7a390040412d43556722b1f9507aa84","tid":1504152,"uid":181627,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T10:59:54.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"915d43b8721c28ae47ab1da4daca8f8d698e8efa","tid":1504152,"uid":204996,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T11:03:26.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c75e98963e347e79808fa03d92b416bd9a20f668","tid":1504152,"uid":140802,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T11:06:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"400c4d63d8fd2d032ee6cd92e2e9083d920ce121","tid":1504152,"uid":222970,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T11:07:59.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://t.me/scottscout2\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fscottscout2&d=6v%2BmLhPCoO19KIzpXGl1Dv2x0mEA6i1FZlyL0j1bjmE%3D&h=287760f2\" target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/scottscout2</a>"},{"pid":"4c06bdb2746096f71fd632e98dc93fd7aaa0c352","tid":1504152,"uid":105905,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score"